    {
      "name": "Orders",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Order",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"numeroPedido\": \"PEDIDO-001\",\n  \"valorTotal\": 350.75,\n  \"dataCriacao\": \"2026-03-09T12:00:00Z\",\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"idItem\": \"101\",\n      \"quantidadeItem\": 2,\n      \"valorItem\": 125.25\n    },\n    {\n      \"idItem\": \"102\",\n      \"quantidadeItem\": 1,\n      \"valorItem\": 100.25\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/order",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["order"]
            },
            "description": "Cria um novo pedido no sistema.\n\n**Requer:** Token JWT\n\n**Transformação de dados:**\n- numeroPedido → orderId\n- valorTotal → value\n- dataCriacao → creationDate\n- items.idItem → items.productId\n- items.quantidadeItem → items.quantity\n- items.valorItem → items.price\n\n**Campos obrigatórios:**\n- numeroPedido (string)\n- valorTotal (number)\n- dataCriacao (ISO 8601 date)\n- items (array, não vazio)\n  - idItem (string)\n  - quantidadeItem (number)\n  - valorItem (number)\n\n**Response (201):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Order created successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"numeroPedido\": \"PEDIDO-001\",\n    \"valorTotal\": 350.75,\n    \"dataCriacao\": \"2026-03-09T12:00:00.000Z\",\n    \"items\": [...]\n  }\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "Authorization",
                    "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"numeroPedido\": \"PEDIDO-001\",\n  \"valorTotal\": 350.75,\n  \"dataCriacao\": \"2026-03-09T12:00:00Z\",\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"idItem\": \"101\",\n      \"quantidadeItem\": 2,\n      \"valorItem\": 125.25\n    }\n  ]\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/order",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["order"]
                }
              },
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Order created successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"numeroPedido\": \"PEDIDO-001\",\n    \"valorTotal\": 350.75,\n    \"dataCriacao\": \"2026-03-09T12:00:00.000Z\",\n    \"items\": [\n      {\n        \"idItem\": \"101\",\n        \"quantidadeItem\": 2,\n        \"valorItem\": 125.25\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Error - Validation",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
